Shadow Hand (Counter)
Level: Swordsage 8, Saint 8
Prerequisite: Three Shadow Hand maneuvers
Initiation Action: 1 immediate action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: Six seconds

As an immediate action, you gain the defensive immunities of an incorporeal undead creature, along with being able to move through other creatures and 50% concealment.  You remain in this state until the beginning of your next turn.
